					<strike>In order to use any of these services, you will need to authenticate either with a BrowserID account or a local Arch Linux account, depending on the type of service. Please be aware that every single service here is broken for various reasons, except for SSH.</strike> Almost everything on this page is inaccurate, and I can&apos;t be bothered to update it. I&apos;ll probably get around to it when I finish rewriting the build backend for this site.
